If you can think it, you can build it with this app for kids. Assemble voice disguisers, kaleidoscopes, alarms, and more with plenty of guidance that will get makers of all ages up and running.

If you can think it, you can build it with The Everything Machine. Designed for kids, Tinybops latest innovation lets you combine the camera, microphone and other hardware features of iPhone and iPad to create machines of all kinds. Kids will delight in assembling voice disguisers, kaleidoscopes, alarms that trigger if someone dares to swipe a prized possession and more. The intuitive, image-based programming language makes it simple to connect parts onscreen, and the app offers plenty of guidance and inspiration to get makers of all ages up and running.
